===Baryanting Filipino===
Ligaya king Ibpa, at king Anak, at King Espiritu Santo<br>
Anti mo ing sadya nang ligaya Ibat king kamumulan<br>
Ngeni at kapilan man Mangga man king alang angga,<br>
Amen.

===Baryanting Espanyol===
Ligaya qñg Ibpa, at qñg Anac, at qñg Espiritu Santo<br>
Antimo ing sadia nang ligaya ibat qñg camumulan<br>
Ngeni't capilan man, mangga man qñg alang angga,<br>
Amen.

